Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat(chat): prompt shortcut, layout fix, child avatar,
 profile lock, discard

- "prompt: <text>" in the chat input bypasses Luna's conversation and
  calls generate-story directly with mode "prompt", then jumps to Script
- Layout: removed fixed-height container so the input appears immediately
  below the last message instead of floating at the bottom of the screen
- User message bubbles now show the selected child's avatar emoji on the right
- First user message locks the child profile picker (ChildProfilePicker gains
  a disabled prop); picker unlocks when profile is manually changed or chat
  is discarded
- Discard button appears after the first user message; requires inline
  confirmation before wiping the chat and restarting the greeting

